<P><FONT size=3><STRONG>Wireless Hot Spots</STRONG></FONT></P>
<P>A wireless hot spot is a new phrase that describes 802.11b areas or regions where connectivity to the internet is available. Usually in a small radius such as arount an airport, hotel, marina etc.</P>
